channel.title: New [showoff] from scratch. DAGANORTH PLATE. Gamerzonline production!
channel.description:
Hi im here with another showoff, this time its just a plate. Its not a recolour its not a leech, but its from scratch sorry to say.
Yes I know its not perfect but even the best modelest doesn't always create perfect designs. [IMG]http://i438.photobucket.com/albums/qq110/Mason_013/DaganorthArmourlines.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i438.photobucket.com/albums/qq110/Mason_013/DaganorthArmour.jpg[/img]
I am going to work on this later on in the future.
